    "description": "<p>Here at Hvala, we aspire to create a community space for people to gather at and spark conversations over tea. We believe in curation - be it in terms of the spaces that we are in, the tea that we source, or the art pieces we display.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>To us, people development is eminently important. At the core of our company is our people, and we seek to have them progress in tandem with thier individual life goals.&nbsp;</p>",
